template : path value index shape color arrowOrientation edgeLabelLeftOrRight "bottomLabel "sideLabel "edgeLabel
example : r0a2b1c1d1 1 13 s r ab el "l1 (c3, c4) "l2 (c1) "l3 left label

path,value,index are required attributes, rest are optionally, the order does not matter, it can be imagined as set of optional arguments
it is possible to add some description of given tree with letter #
#this text will be in description of tree

ATTRIBUTE		        DOMAIN					                SHORTCUTS	    DEFAULT VALUES
shape	 		        { circle, square }  		            { c }		    square
color	 		        { red, blank, black } 		            { r, b }	    black
arrowOrientation	    { toNode, fromNode, bothDirections }	{ at, af, ab }	no arrow
edgeLabelLeftOrRight    { left, right }                         { el, er }      no edge label

attributes explanation:

path : path containing all nodes on the way to given node(in order from root to given node)
value : value representing given node in the tree
index : defines the appearance order of nodes
shape : shape of the node
color : color of the node
arrowOrientation : direction of edge
edgeLabelLeftOrRight : edge label location, 2 options left or right side of the edge
buttonLabel : name of label under the node
sideLabel : name of label on the right side of the node
edgeLabel : edge label name